<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <title>발주 취소 | iM캐피탈 관리자</title>

    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/static/admin/css/admin.css">


    <script src="/static/web/js/lib/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/static/admin/js/admin_popup.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
    function addrPopupAll() {
        uiCommon.openPopup("addrPopup");
    }
</script>

<a href="javascript:;" class="popup-btn" onclick="addrPopupAll();return false;">팝업 버튼</a>

<div class="dim dim-02"></div>

<div class="popup-layer" id="addrPopup">
    <div class="popup popup-01"><!-- [D]작은 팝업인 경우 : popup-half(가로 560px) / 큰인 팝업인 경우 : popup-full(가로 1020px) -->
        <div class="inner">
            <div class="popup-text">
                <h1>발주 취소</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="popup-contents"><!-- 부모창 스크롤 없는 경우 클래스 추가 : no-scroll -->

                <!-- Start : content //-->
                <h2>발주를 취소하시겠습니까?<br>취소 사유를 작성해주세요.</h2>
                <table class="data-tbl mt30">
                    <colgroup>
                        <col width="50%">
                        <col width="50%">
                    </colgroup>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2">
                                <div class="com-inp">
                                    <p class="tit ver-top">취소사유</p>
                                    <textarea style="height: 112px;" placeholder="내용 입력"></textarea>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                
                <!-- Start : 버튼 //-->
                <div class="btn-area">
                    <a href="#" class="gray">취소</a><a href="#">확인</a><!-- [D] 버튼 비활성화인 경우 : 클래스 gray 추가 -->
                </div>
                <!-- //End : 버튼 -->

                <!-- //End : content -->

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="popup-close"><a href="javascript:;"><img src="/static/admin/img/new_common/ico_close.png"></a></div>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>